  <h4 style=3D"margin-left:40px;white-space:pre-wrap;">Consider Accommodati=
on Alternatives</h4><p class=3D"" style=3D"white-space:pre-wrap;">I have st=
ayed in many hotels during my career. For me, luxury was delightful when it=
 wasn=E2=80=99t out of my pocket but after a while, I noticed that big hote=
ls have a standardized feel.&nbsp; I remember staying in a lovely luxury ho=
tel in Ottawa, thinking I could be in Vancouver, London, California, or any=
where! It was very nice but had limited local personality. On my own dime, =
I am continuing to explore alternative accommodation options to both save a=
 substantial amount of money AND make my travels unique, interesting, and w=
ith a local flair.<br><br>Accommodation has the potential to be the biggest=
 percentage of a travel budget. On a 10-week trip to Spain and Portugal, we=
 made choices that brought this down considerably, leaving more for activit=
ies (and buying Christmas presents!). On the trip we:</p><ul data-rte-list=
=3D"default"><li><p class=3D"" style=3D"white-space:pre-wrap;">Used reward =
points for 5 nights</p></li><li><p class=3D"" style=3D"white-space:pre-wrap=
;">Received incredible discounts of 40%off for two, month-long bookings</p>=
</li><li><p class=3D"" style=3D"white-space:pre-wrap;">Stayed for free on a=
 spontaneous week-long side trip to France using Home Exchange&nbsp;</p></l=
i></ul><p class=3D"" style=3D"white-space:pre-wrap;">In an upcoming trip to=
 the UK and France, we are paying =E2=80=9Creal money=E2=80=9D for 6 nights=
 out of 21. The rest are a combination of <a href=3D"https://www.homeexchan=
ge.com/" target=3D"_blank" data-modified-href=3D"https://www.homeexchange.c=
om/">Home Exchange,</a> reward nights, and 3 nights at a friend=E2=80=99s h=
ome.</p><p style=3D"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class=3D"sqsrt=
e-large"><a href=3D"https://www.travelbugtonic.com/blog/how-does-home-excha=
nge-work" target=3D"_blank" data-modified-href=3D"https://www.travelbugtoni=
c.com/blog/how-does-home-exchange-work"><span class=3D"sqsrte-text-color--a=
ccent"><strong>Curious about Home Exchange? Read this article!</strong></sp=
an></a></p><p class=3D"" style=3D"white-space:pre-wrap;">Also consider pet =
or house sitting, workaways, volunteer gigs, or other creative ways to stay=
 for less or for free.&nbsp;</p>
</div>




















