<div class=3D"sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content=3D"">
  <h3 style=3D"white-space:pre-wrap;"><strong>4. Saving Money on Activities=
: Having Fun!</strong></h3><h4 style=3D"margin-left:40px;white-space:pre-wr=
ap;">Be Selective with Tours</h4><p class=3D"" style=3D"white-space:pre-wra=
p;">We value the depth that having a local guide provides, but due to the e=
xpense, we pick and choose where and when we want to take advantage of them=
. If it is a high priority, the information from a local guide is incredibl=
e! For example, we went up Mt. Etna with a local geologist who offered a co=
mpletely unique perspective. It was an excellent experience and worth every=
 Euro. The tour also included lunch and transportation, so we also solved o=
ur challenge of how to get up a volcano with no car!&nbsp;<br><br>We very m=
uch enjoy and utilize audio guides. If there is a free <a href=3D"https://w=
ww.ricksteves.com/watch-read-listen/audio/audio-tours" target=3D"_blank" da=
ta-modified-href=3D"https://www.ricksteves.com/watch-read-listen/audio/audi=
o-tours">Rick Steves audio tour</a>, we use it!&nbsp; <a href=3D"https://ww=
w.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=3D99601&amp;awinaffid=3D2089825&amp;ued=3Dhtt=
ps%3A%2F%2Fvoicemap.me%2F" target=3D"_blank" data-modified-href=3D"https://=
voicemap.me/?source=3Daw&amp;utm_source=3Dawin&amp;aw_affid=3D2089825&amp;a=
wc=3D99601_1754869898_75e07b57c16deab040e489d058c10a1f">VoiceMap</a> is ano=
ther low-cost audio tour option developed by local guides. Free walking tou=
rs are a favourite too, although we always pay as it is a tip-based service=
 and I=E2=80=99ve never been disappointed!<br><br>We pay (and sometimes a l=
ot) for special experiences that we identify as important to us. A Flamenco=
 Show, a European Futbol match, cooking classes, entrance tickets, boat rid=
es, and museums when we=E2=80=99re in the mood. This is where knowing your =
travel intentions along with your unique interests really matter.&nbsp;</p>
</div>




















